<div class="jumbotron" style="margin-top: 2%;">
    <h1 class="display-3">The Colby Jitney Service
    </h1>
    <p class="lead">What Is The Jitney?</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p>The Colby Jitney is a free shuttle service available to students.
            It takes students from Colby to Waterville locations on a first-come,
            first serve basis. The Jitney service employs student drivers and a
            student program supervisor. During operating hours it can be found
            outside the Pugh Center waiting to pick up students if not out in
            town picking up and dropping off at countless places. The Jitney
            drivers, student supervisors, and Security Department all work together
            to provide a quality customer experience to the Colby Community. Call
            the Security Office to see if it is running at 207-859-5530.</p>
    <p class="lead">
        <button class="btn  btn-lg"> Request A Ride </button>
    </p>
